track.name: I and I Survive
comments: Listen, no, not I...I and I will never try....try to live that way!

There's one Bad brains track that is rather homophobic: 'Blowing Bubbles'. The band said they wrote it cos they were trying to warn people to stop having unprotected gay sex and catching AIDs. This song is definitely not homophobic and now one of the members of the band admitted that they used to be homophobic but not anymore x
I and I will never try...
Does last let you hear the song??
Sometimes I wish if there would be a full on Roots album by this band. Having the Dub album is cool and all but a whole roots album would kick ass. Just imagine this song x 12.
REG-CORE KICKING ASS  HAVE JAMMED TO THEM FOR MANY YEARS
"i" - jah, Jehovah, the one, - "and I" - myself, me the believer - "will survive"
